":2125383,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cd9893df079d450231e73bdc20992bf2bf6fc189","tid":2125383,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T07:04:58.000Z","msg":"暴風雨前既寧靜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T07:16:14.000Z","msg":"勁過山竹？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T09:11:37.000Z","msg":"冇乜夏颱嘅風季通常秋颱都OK強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勁過山竹&hellip;&hellip;需要天時地利人和<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.因為海水比較暖，夏秋季颱風能量多D就勁D<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.嗰個地方風切變比較弱+水氣多D就會令颱風少D出意外即係減弱咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.如果颱風顛峰時間keep得比較短又喺遠洋冇實測嘅地方上peak，係各大氣象台(如日本氣象廳、中央氣象台、聯合颱風警報中心)出report之前已經減弱咗，你幾勁都冇人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9c2d1122ba6ea264032091546910ac083212a7","tid":2125383,"uid":352783,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T11:06:19.000Z","msg":"邊個咁得閑個個comment負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c248c5c6f0fd0eb275ad2a1d6399bf992d4199b7","tid":2125383,"uid":72725,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T04:28:05.000Z","msg":"前排觀塘先水浸完"}]}